name: Wrath of the king
description: Big Business people create viruses and even drugs to maximize profits. People are forced to consume it because they have no other choice. Again, the victims are weak and helpless humans and Nature. Nature conditions and ecosystems on earth are getting worse and worse because many humans only think about profit, sacrificing other parties who are weak and don't think about the continuity of life on this earth. They are humans but don't have humanity.
